"},{"pid":"ad90dce169563ca9502509014bc623139db2337f","tid":1898380,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:37:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭理財新哲學就係玩到香港財赤然後派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c83dfb553ef25e5b582d622d42a4a89bf5bed1","tid":1898380,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"又多一推新移民可以攞到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90001e07c817306934899034400ffcb46884235","tid":1898380,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7fcffb7723ade99f3eacadf7caa683f98ea50f9","tid":1898380,"uid":199252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"幾時可以申請"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"問：申領1萬元的資格？<br />\n答：申請人需要在2021年3月31日或之前成為香港永久性居民，以及年滿18歲，即需要於2003年3月31日出生。<br />\n<br />\n問：何時開始申請？何時能收錢？<br />\n答：政府消息人士指參考2011年派發6000港元做法，期望8月底前開放申請，計劃按年齡組群分批申請，最快明年2月能夠收取款項。"},{"pid":"7f09800da14d12ec5928324892e00fef3c2829bb","tid":1898380,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"佢交個波俾立法會，拉布啦。"},{"pid":"3ce992630932e7ce5c743361e3e0954a8aaefd96","tid":1898380,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d984aa278befe43cb420682e23a9025258dde91e","tid":1898380,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"呢家先年頭<br />\n重等下年年尾 舒咩困"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:38:40.000Z","msg":"佢係話去到下年先停申請<br />\n下年3月尾前十八歲人士都可以申請"}]}